  <h2>
    <span class="">这本书的其他版本 </span>
      &nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;&middot;
      <span class="pl">&nbsp;(
          <a href="https://book.douban.com/works/1015828">全部6</a>
        ) </span>

  </h2>


  <div class="indent">
    <ul>
        <li class="mb8 pl">
          <a href="https://book.douban.com/subject/26701963/">上海文艺出版社版</a>
          2016-5-1 / 100人读过 / 有售
        </li>
        <li class="mb8 pl">
          <a href="https://book.douban.com/subject/2471992/">Picador版</a>
          2003-6-1 / 2人读过
